        <h1>Astro + Spin</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">An Astro website, running as a <a href="https://spinframework.dev/" class="text-white" target="_blank">Spin</a> WebAssembly app, deployed to <a href="https://www.fermyon.com/wasm-functions" class="text-white" target="_blank">Fermyon Wasm Functions</a></p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>âš¡ Fast</h3>
                <p>Zero JS by default for lightning-fast loading</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>ðŸ”§ Flexible</h3>
                <p>Use any framework or vanilla HTML/CSS/JS</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>ðŸŽ¯ Modern</h3>
                <p>Built for the modern web with great DX</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/fermyon/spin-astro" target="_blank"><button class="cta-button" class="text-white">View on GitHub</button></a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>